author: @stephanielemons2995
text: I have noticed something about Kai... there are two of him. Let me explain, I have seen many Rover challenges with many different k pop idols and Kai, and with the exception of two other idols, Kai holds back on his dancing with all the other idols to allow them to match their styles. However, when it comes to members of his own group or Taemin, Jimin, or Momo, Kai doesn't hold back because he knows that they can keep up with him if he goes all out. It just shows me that there are two sides to him, and both have mad respect for every other idol out there.
